Item.Code: Calculation Skew Attribution OTC Vega Exposure

CellDefinition.Value: NOT(ISERROR(Lowerpoint)) AND NOT(ISERROR(Upperpoint)) AND nearestMaturity<OTCExpiry AND longestmaturity>OTCExpiry

ItemList(DatabaseName,Item(DatabaseName,VolaStructure,"Front Arena Equity Volatility Surface").Surfacepoints.Data(StartDate)).Where(Code LIKE '*'+ skew1.TOSTRING('dd.MM.yyyy') +'*' OR (IF(case1 OR case4,TRUE,Code LIKE '*'+ skew2.TOSTRING('dd.MM.yyyy') +'*')) ).Where(|option| <> NULL).Values(option,VolaStructure,Maturity.Data(StartDate),strike,|diff to settle|.Data(StartDate)).SORT(4)

IF(ISERROR(skew1Leftoption) AND NOT(ISERROR(skew1Rightoption)),DiffSettle1L, IF(NOT(ISERROR(skew1Leftoption)) AND ISERROR(skew1Rightoption),DiffSettle1R,IF(NOT(ISERROR(skew1Leftoption)) AND NOT(ISERROR(skew1Rightoption)) AND skew1Leftoption <> skew1Rightoption,DiffSettle1L+(OTCStrike - Strike1L)*(DiffSettle1R-DiffSettle1L)/(Strike1R-Strike1L),NA())))

IF(ISERROR(skew2Leftoption) AND NOT(ISERROR(skew2Rightoption)),DiffSettle2L, IF(NOT(ISERROR(skew2Leftoption)) AND ISERROR(skew2Rightoption),DiffSettle2R,IF(NOT(ISERROR(skew2Leftoption)) AND NOT(ISERROR(skew2Rightoption)) AND skew2Leftoption <> skew2Rightoption,DiffSettle2L+(OTCStrike - Strike2L)*(DiffSettle2R-DiffSettle2L)/(Strike2R-Strike2L),NA())))
[Expiry] of OTC Vega Exposure = the nearest [Maturity] of FA_VolSkews
[Expiry] of "OTC Vega Exposure" >= the longest [Maturity] of "FA_VolSkews"
